- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper involves natural language processing techniques for speaker recognition. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper proposes a machine learning method for unsupervised speaker recognition. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques for unsupervised speaker recognition. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although the paper is not directly related to computer vision, the multilayer bootstrap network used in the proposed method can be considered as a pattern recognition technique.
